abstract: >-
  Zero-multiply language generation engine using permutation table lookups
  and integer accumulation. Achieves 18,000 tokens/second with 0.3-3 MB models.
  Introduces cache-resonance attention, NUMA-aware cell banking, and dual-brain
  speculative drafting for LLMs. Runs on Nintendo 64 through IBM POWER8.
